WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: uz

00:00:00.312 --> 00:00:03.562
Mayli, endi oldinga boramiz va
matnni oq rangga o‘zgartiramiz.

00:00:03.562 --> 00:00:06.400
Hammasi yaxshi, avvalgidek
atribut yoki xususiyatlarni tanlang,

00:00:06.400 --> 00:00:10.210
rangni oq rangga o‘zgartiradi deb 
o‘ylagan katakchalarni ishlatib.

00:00:10.210 --> 00:00:12.290
SUBMIT orqali javobingizni tekshiring va

00:00:12.290 --> 00:00:14.650
siz to‘g‘ri atributlarni tanlay bilganingizda,

00:00:14.650 --> 00:00:19.649
Men qiymatni @android:color/white ga o‘zgartirishingizni xohlayman

00:00:19.649 --> 00:00:23.120
Davom eting buni ikkala 
 TextView uchun bajaring.

00:00:23.120 --> 00:00:26.920
Endi ushbu oraliq bosqichda, sizning 
ilovangiz biroz kulgili ko‘rinishi mumkin.

00:00:26.920 --> 00:00:29.910
Siz aynan oq fonga egasiz
va siz unga oq matnni qo‘yyapsiz.

00:00:29.910 --> 00:00:32.070
Bunda matningizni ko‘rish 
qiyin bo‘lishi aniq.

00:00:32.070 --> 00:00:33.900
